<h1>
  Class TaskSynchronization
</h1>
<pre>
java.lang.Object
   |
   +----TaskSynchronization
</pre>
<hr>
<dl>
  <dt> public class <b>TaskSynchronization</b>
  <dt> extends Object
</dl>
Task synchronization monitor.
 <strong>Task synchronization monitors in the same job should always
 be disjoint.</strong>
<p>
<hr>
